overview: The Doctor needs a huge favor from Jazy and she's not too pleased. Lucky for her a good deed goes a long, long way. Nurse Jaymes is fed up working double shifts and has it out with her boss. The two find a way to get exactly what they want. It's Nurse Jenna's first day at the hospital. So she gets the royal tour by the head surgeon. Most importantly: The Relaxation Room. Nurse Kagney has to deal with a bitchy wife who blames her husband for his lack of sex drive. But Kagney knows best how to cure that.
title: A Nurse's Touch
